modules.description: Converts between bit vector representations and S-expressions. Works with `Bitvec_sexp.t` and `Sexplib0.Sexp.t` types. Useful for serializing and deserializing bit vectors to and from textual S-expression formats, enabling data persistence and interchange.

Converts bit vectors to and from S-expressions for serialization and parsing. Works directly with `Bitvec.t` and `Sexplib0.Sexp.t` types. Enables saving bit vector data to files or transmitting it over networks in a structured text format.
